      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 44-49.</p><p>Powerful Reserve</p><p>Also at 24th level, you can push your limits even when there is nothing more to give. If you have 0 Legendary Points, you can still use a feature that costs 1 Legendary Point. If you do so, the next time you use the Recover action, it does not restore any Legendary Points.</p></div>",
